    <h2 class="content__title">
      Details
    </h2>

    <ul class="body-copy">
      <li><strong>Talks should be 30 minutes long</strong>, with time allowed afterward for Q&amp;A.</li>
      <li>There will be 8 speakers selected for the event.</li>
      <li>The event will be held in Saddlers Well's Theatre, Islington, London.</li>
      <li>We may be able to cover your travel expenses, please get in touch if you'd like to know more.</li>
    </ul>

